title: The Falling Soldier - Wikipedia
snippet:
The Falling Soldier is a photograph by Robert Capa, claimed to have been taken 
on Saturday, September 5, 1936. It was said to depict the death of a Republican 
Iberian Federation of Libertarian Youth (FIJL) soldier, during the Battle of Cerro 
Muriano in the Spanish Civil War.
